description: AP-05 is the legacy RTO code for East Godavari district (headquarters in Kakinada) in Andhra Pradesh. Since February 2019, the state implemented the 'one state-one code' policy where all new vehicles are registered with AP-39/AP-40 series. This office continues to manage legacy AP-05 registrations.
address: RTO Office, Kakinada-Pithapuram Road, Near Collectorate, Kakinada, East Godavari, Andhra Pradesh
